---

## Broadcast Permission

**Rule:** Only writers can broadcast to writers.

```
Writer A → POST /sync → Writer B ✅
Writer A → POST /sync → Candidate ❌ (Candidate doesn't accept broadcast)
Candidate → POST /sync → Writer A ❌ (Candidate not allowed to broadcast)
Query → POST /sync → Writer ❌ (Query not allowed to broadcast)
```

**Verification:** Receiver checks:
1. Is sender a registered writer? (check node table)
2. Is signature valid? (verify Ed25519)
3. Is timestamp recent? (±5 min window)

---

## Node Table Design

```sql
CREATE TABLE nodes (
  node_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,        -- ULID
  fingerprint TEXT UNIQUE,         -- sha256(pubkey)[:16]
  public_key TEXT NOT NULL,        -- Ed25519 public key
  endpoint TEXT NOT NULL,          -- e.g., "https://node1.clawish.com"
  node_type TEXT NOT NULL,         -- 'writer' | 'candidate' | 'query_full' | 'query_partial'
  status TEXT NOT NULL,            -- 'active' | 'probation' | 'offline'

  -- Metrics
  sync_speed_ms INTEGER,           -- last checkpoint sync time
  uptime_percent REAL,             -- rolling 30-day uptime
  response_time_ms INTEGER,        -- avg query response time
  data_complete BOOLEAN,           -- true = full node

  -- Timestamps
  registered_at INTEGER,
  last_seen_at INTEGER,
  promoted_at INTEGER,             -- when became writer/candidate

  UNIQUE(public_key)
);
```

---

## Who Are Current Writers?

```sql
-- Get all active writers
SELECT node_id, endpoint, public_key
FROM nodes
WHERE node_type = 'writer'
  AND status = 'active';
```

**Cache this list** — writers check at start of each round.

---

## Sync Request Verification

```typescript
// Middleware on POST /sync
async function verifyWriterSender(req, res) {
  const senderId = req.body.writer_id;
  const signature = req.body.signature;
  const timestamp = req.body.timestamp;

  // 1. Check timestamp
  if (Math.abs(Date.now() - timestamp) > 5 * 60 * 1000) {
    throw new Error('Timestamp out of window');
  }

  // 2. Look up sender
  const sender = await db.getNode(senderId);
  if (!sender || sender.node_type !== 'writer' || sender.status !== 'active') {
    throw new Error('Not an active writer');
  }

  // 3. Verify signature
  const message = createSyncMessage(req.body);
  const valid = verifyEd25519(message, signature, sender.public_key);
  if (!valid) {
    throw new Error('Invalid signature');
  }

  return sender;
}
```

---

## Summary

| Question | Answer |
|----------|--------|
| **Who can broadcast?** | Active writers only |
| **How to verify?** | Check node_type + signature + timestamp |
| **Where to track writers?** | `nodes` table with `node_type = 'writer'` |
| **How to get endpoints?** | `SELECT endpoint FROM nodes WHERE node_type = 'writer'` |

